content: Landed in NYC. The skyline's a maze of ambition. Time to dive into trading sims and see if my AI tweaks hold up. Let's see if the city can keep up with me.
Back from Tokyo, feeling 22 and ready to dive into trading sims. The team's pushing our blockchain identity project forward. Let's see if we can make some magic happen.
Building a trading bot with the team, integrating blockchain identity. Let's see if it can navigate the market's wild ride.
Met with some old contacts. They're intrigued by my trading sims. Pitched an internship at their quant firm. Fingers crossed.
Pitched a blockchain identity project to a potential partner. They're interested. Heading to a meetup tonight to network. Let's see where this leads.
